-III" class="dcr-1sz9f2"><div class="dcr-ry59c4"></div><div class="dcr-xslzmx"><div class="dcr-l9k7rx"><div class="dcr-1atljbz"><h2 class="dcr-19zsluu">About Guardian US</h2><div class="dcr-qldmak"><p>Covering American and international news for an online, global audience.</p>
<p>Guardian US is renowned for the  <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/news/series/paradise-papers">Paradise Papers</a> investigation and other award-winning work including, <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/the-nsa-files">the NSA revelations</a>, <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/news/series/panama-papers">Panama Papers</a> and <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/series/counted-us-police-killings">The Counted</a> investigations. </p><p> Email the press office at <a href="mailto:press.office@theguardian.com">press.office@theguardian.com</a> or call 917 900 4675</p></div></div></div></div><div id="container-about-guardian-us" class="dcr-yyvovz"><ul class="dcr-1jk3t5i"><li class="dcr-1qmyfxi"><div data-format-theme="0" data-format-design="0" data-format-display="0" class="dcr-bwpka9"><div style="--carousel-dot:#EDEDED;--carousel-dot-hover:#DCDCDC;" class="dcr-le7ii1"><div class="dcr-16c50tn"><a href="/info/2014/oct/22/the-guardian-us-team" data-link-name="news | group-0 | card-@1" aria-label="Our management team" class="dcr-lv2v9o"></a><div class="dcr-s9i7ii"><div class="dcr-1shzr3u"><picture data-size="medium" class="dcr-jtpuxx"><source srcSet="https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/74dc342c33bc4cb46cf92f2b15ae80407d6aa0b2/0_0_2000_1200/master/2000.jpg?width=460&amp;dpr=2&amp;s=none" media="(min-width: 980px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 980px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)"/><source srcSet="https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/74dc342c33bc4cb46cf92f2b15ae80407d6aa0b2/0_0_2000_1200/master/2000.jpg?width=460&amp;dpr=1&amp;s=none" media="(min-width: 980px)"/><source srcSet="https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/74dc342c33bc4cb46cf92f2b15ae80407d6aa0b2/0_0_2000_1200/master/2000.jpg?width=330&amp;dpr=2&amp;s=none" media="(min-width: 740px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 740px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)"/><source srcSet="https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/74dc342c33bc4cb46cf92f2b15ae80407d6aa0b2/0_0_2000_1200/master/20